  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>QUINTILLIONS OF BULLETS AGAINST QUINTILLIONS OF ALIEN CHAOS</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survivors of the Dawn is a rogue-lite horde-survival bullet heaven. Bombard <strong>QUINTILLIONS of hordes with QUINTILLIONS of bullets</strong>! Mix weapons with items, modify, control chaos at terminals and break through tightening waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MODIFY, MAX OUT, TAKE RISKS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want bigger attacks? or Need the shots to go through more enemies? <strong>Bullet Count</strong> and <strong>Pierce</strong> comes to the rescue! Get items and modify your weapons in the <strong>Armory.</strong> You can also fire faster with <strong>Bullet Speed</strong> or reduce <strong>Reload Time</strong>. Max out weapons in the <strong>Upgrade System</strong>. Meanwhile, take risks for higher rewards with the <strong>Rarity System</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/5417d1b41029d8be24e324ceac9ef8a5.poster.avif?t=1765396692\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/5417d1b41029d8be24e324ceac9ef8a5.webm?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/5417d1b41029d8be24e324ceac9ef8a5.mp4?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MIX WEAPONS WITH ITEMS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up weapons, stack items, mix and match to <strong>WIPE OUT</strong> hordes. Oh, extra allies or sparkly power-ups? Just max out some weapon classes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/f3aafa0625801abf8ba3b2829d7a894d.poster.avif?t=1765396692\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/f3aafa0625801abf8ba3b2829d7a894d.webm?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/f3aafa0625801abf8ba3b2829d7a894d.mp4?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GO ALL IN ON TERMINALS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feeling overwhelmed? Activate the S.O.S to catch your breath. Craving more action? Summon extra hordes at <strong>Wanted</strong>. Tag along with the Spider bot to heal, and react to the <strong>Unknown Signal </strong>for more or less dificulty and find some <strong><i>Reroll or Skip</i></strong> chances if lucky enough!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/c736d1d2b9f947fdb76c37d4358239b9.poster.avif?t=1765396692\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/c736d1d2b9f947fdb76c37d4358239b9.webm?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/c736d1d2b9f947fdb76c37d4358239b9.mp4?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh, boy... Meta-progression is far from guaranteed unless you spend your <i><strong>Bounty Bits</strong></i> before your next run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >indieGiant Games is a <i>micro</i> studio with <strong>massive</strong> ideas based in Istanbul, Türkiye. We make games that we are excited to play and share them with you.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>QUINTILLIONS OF BULLETS AGAINST QUINTILLIONS OF ALIEN CHAOS</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survivors of the Dawn is a rogue-lite horde-survival bullet heaven. Bombard <strong>QUINTILLIONS of hordes with QUINTILLIONS of bullets</strong>! Mix weapons with items, modify, control chaos at terminals and break through tightening waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MODIFY, MAX OUT, TAKE RISKS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want bigger attacks? or Need the shots to go through more enemies? <strong>Bullet Count</strong> and <strong>Pierce</strong> comes to the rescue! Get items and modify your weapons in the <strong>Armory.</strong> You can also fire faster with <strong>Bullet Speed</strong> or reduce <strong>Reload Time</strong>. Max out weapons in the <strong>Upgrade System</strong>. Meanwhile, take risks for higher rewards with the <strong>Rarity System</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/5417d1b41029d8be24e324ceac9ef8a5.poster.avif?t=1765396692\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/5417d1b41029d8be24e324ceac9ef8a5.webm?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/5417d1b41029d8be24e324ceac9ef8a5.mp4?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MIX WEAPONS WITH ITEMS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up weapons, stack items, mix and match to <strong>WIPE OUT</strong> hordes. Oh, extra allies or sparkly power-ups? Just max out some weapon classes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/f3aafa0625801abf8ba3b2829d7a894d.poster.avif?t=1765396692\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/f3aafa0625801abf8ba3b2829d7a894d.webm?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/f3aafa0625801abf8ba3b2829d7a894d.mp4?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GO ALL IN ON TERMINALS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feeling overwhelmed? Activate the S.O.S to catch your breath. Craving more action? Summon extra hordes at <strong>Wanted</strong>. Tag along with the Spider bot to heal, and react to the <strong>Unknown Signal </strong>for more or less dificulty and find some <strong><i>Reroll or Skip</i></strong> chances if lucky enough!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/c736d1d2b9f947fdb76c37d4358239b9.poster.avif?t=1765396692\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/c736d1d2b9f947fdb76c37d4358239b9.webm?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/c736d1d2b9f947fdb76c37d4358239b9.mp4?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh, boy... Meta-progression is far from guaranteed unless you spend your <i><strong>Bounty Bits</strong></i> before your next run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >indieGiant Games is a <i>micro</i> studio with <strong>massive</strong> ideas based in Istanbul, Türkiye. We make games that we are excited to play and share them with you.</p>",
